The paper discusses the challenges of writing and maintaining software documentation, which is a common problem in software engineering (cs.SE). The proposed solution involves using a controlled natural language (cs.CL) with a reasoner and query engine, which suggests a focus on programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also presents positive results on the comprehensibility and feasibility of creating and verifying documentation, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG).
